'''A_FirePhoenixPL1'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Fires a {{Class|PhoenixFX1}} and adjusts the player's horizontal velocity backwards by 4 units, simulating a strong recoil.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|PhoenixRod}} and derived classes.

